SORCERY

Linked Attribute: ^gWillpower^n

Skill in sorcery is vital if you have magical ability and wish to cast ^Wspells^n.
With it, you are able to manipulate magical energies and control them in the
form of ^Wspells^n.

Also

Usage: ^gORDER <spirit> SORCERY^n

This command is used when you want an elemental to assist you with casting
your next spell. Elementals can only be assist a spell of the same domain.

Elemental Domains:
  Fire - Combat  
  Air - Detection 
  Water - Illusion
  Earth - Manipulation

^WSee Also: CONJURING, CASTING, ORDER^n

